com.here.android.mpa.urbanmobility

Enum TransportType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TransportType>
      • com.here.android.mpa.urbanmobility.TransportType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TransportType>

    public enum TransportType
extends java.lang.Enum<TransportType>
    Represents possible types of transit to be included in the response.

    IMPORTANT: Urban Mobility is a Beta feature. The related classes are subject to change without notice.
